lead_paragraph: Scott Brown and Phil Mickelson both had reason to believe it could be a long day on the South Course at Torrey Pines. It turned out just fine Thursday in the Farmers Insurance Open, especially for Brown.

headline.print_headline: Brown Handles South to Share Early Lead at Torrey Pines
